    {
      "description": "Looking and planning further ahead, and doing so in a strategic and cost-effective manner, is key to achieving National Grid\u2019s vision of being at the heart of a clean, fair and affordable energy future. The data in this section provides insights into assumptions for future demand growth under various scenarios (DFES), network constraints and solutions identified over a 10-year period (NDP), and network investment decisions following cost benefit analysis and flexibility procurement, where applicable (DNOA).",
